creator: Mood13
descriptionHtml:
Mood 13 Magazine is a Taylor Swift-inspired digital magazine for Swifties featuring projects, DIY, crafts, recipes, parties, and more.

The brainchild of a Swiftie mom with an eye for interior design, Mood 13 Magazine is a fun and engaging combination of crafting, entertaining, and home decor that has the sophistication of a traditional DIY magazine with the vibrant aesthetic of all things Taylor Swift. This is a magazine for Swifties by Swifties that includes project ideas for Swifties of all ages. Not affiliated with Taylor Swift.

Regarding phone number for sign up: The use of a phone number is for the sole purpose of occasional push notifications to alert users of promotions, giveaways and newly published issues. We do not sell private informaiton to third parties or use private information in any way outside of marketing our product. See our privacy page for more information.
